import React from 'react'
import { Card, Image, Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'


function FeaturesCards ({ lHomes }) {

    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col sm={6}>
                        <Card>
                            <Image src={lHomes.last.photos[3].image} fluid />
                        </Card>
                    </Col>

                    <Col sm={6}>
                        <Card>
                            <Image src={lHomes.last.photos[4].image} fluid />
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default FeaturesCards;
